  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DateTimeFormat
    DateTimeFormat Patterns used to parse given date DateTimeUtils will use those pattern
    DateTimeUtils
    DateTimeUtils This class contains a bunch of function that can manipulate Date object or Date String to achieve certain operations e.g : Time difference, Time Ago, Date formatting
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DateTimeStyle
    DateTimeStyle Defined style for parsing date into string used by formatWithStyle(Date, DateTimeStyle) and also getTimeAgo(Context, Date, DateTimeStyle)
    DateTimeUnits
    DateTimeUnits Define units used by getDateDiff(Date, Date, DateTimeUnits) and also formatDate(long, DateTimeUnits)
